{"tid":2431872,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國官媒CGTN獲法國批出牌照 可重新在英歐播放","createTime":"2021-03-04T02:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T05:11:22.000Z","uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fb351d4031c159c89712d63d0dc41d0d21171cf1","tid":2431872,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T02:48:42.000Z","msg":"蘋果全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210304/XEJR7ULGXNFZVCS42Q6AEQ2FJM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210304%2FXEJR7ULGXNFZVCS42Q6AEQ2FJM%2F&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX2jFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=5c14779a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210304%2FXEJR7ULGXNFZVCS42Q6AEQ2FJM%2F&h=978907d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210304/XEJR7ULGXNFZVCS42Q6AEQ2FJM/</a><br />\n<br />\n央視旗下的「中國環球電視網」（CGTN），早前被英國指控由中共控制被撤銷廣播牌照，一度失去在歐洲的播放權，昨日卻獲法國監管部門批出廣播牌照，可再次在英國和歐洲國家播放。<br />\n<br />\n法國媒體主管機關「法國最高視聽委員會」昨日舉行會議，通過CGTN的播放執照申請。據悉，CGTN早在去年12月已經向法國申請牌照。根據規定，只須要符合兩項技術條件，包括通過法國衞星廣播，以及訊號由法國發送，便可獲批牌照，毋須審查廣播內容。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2019/03/25/world/25france-xi-01/merlin_152608296_eaa142c8-96b9-48d6-930e-02c047448896-master1050.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.nyt.com%2Fimages%2F2019%2F03%2F25%2Fworld%2F25france-xi-01%2Fmerlin_152608296_eaa142c8-96b9-48d6-930e-02c047448896-master1050.jpg&h=d698182d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cecd08d366a12e65c6e8f8ce9dade3437fdfd3dd","tid":2431872,"uid":155095,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T02:50:08.000Z","msg":"馬卡龍：聯中制美 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.businessfocus.io/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/11b2902a.jpg?auto=format&amp;w=830&amp;q=100\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.businessfocus.io%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F11b2902a.jpg%3Fauto%3Dformat%26w%3D830%26q%3D100&h=af5d3606&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b491023d5ae0d5cf0351341f8783c183cf98711","tid":2431872,"uid":188176,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T02:50:30.000Z","msg":"法國次次都第一個淪陷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca4471bcf0e788f63d0285b507c1e3c1128776e","tid":2431872,"uid":6497,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"1b491023d5ae0d5cf0351341f8783c183cf98711","tid":2431872,"uid":188176,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T02:50:30.000Z","msg":"法國次次都第一個淪陷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T02:51:54.000Z","msg":"係因為法國個廣播條例好撚鬆<br />\n技術規格夠就播得"},{"pid":"1e3c4119c35276325977d5aceb8cd3b9c2d076aa","tid":2431872,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T02:52:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.dw.com/image/48047356_401.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.dw.com%2Fimage%2F48047356_401.jpg&h=bb016f42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://larvi.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/E-Macron-Xi-Jinping-Novembre-2019.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flarvi.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2FE-Macron-Xi-Jinping-Novembre-2019.jpg&h=1b49b92a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06df21d8b6b1233125a22f56bc584aa3d72750ff","tid":2431872,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T02:55:03.000Z","msg":"恭喜中國！法國大城市開始撤除華為通訊設備<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2428528\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2428528</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"383d6651d31c9f6b2e20417379bea3cc96222178","tid":2431872,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T03:06:03.000Z","msg":"英國幾時脫埋呢條條例"},{"pid":"70f3a01af3e54c4f1183d2e405c8abb86469cec3","tid":2431872,"uid":31215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"